The paper deals with optimization methods for machine learning, specifically logistic regression. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses stochastic and online optimization, which are subfields of optimization and machine learning, respectively. This suggests that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are also likely categories. The paper also involves information theory and statistical inference, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
